- Audit trail complete

✅ **Case Status Confirmed Ready for Matching**
- Case status = READY_FOR_MATCHING
- All validation passed
- Case prepared for WF-003

✅ **WF-003 Can Begin**
- Case is queued for matching
- Professional search can commence

