- ARCHITECTURE_PRINCIPLES.md (Single Source of Truth, Domain-First Design)
- DOMAIN_MODEL_DATABASE_SPEC.md (SessionLog and RegisteredHours entities)
- DECISION_LOG.md (Decision #4)

