  Padding/margin scale
```

### Implementation in Match 2.0
```
/shared/design-system/
├─ colors.ts
├─ typography.ts
├─ tailwind.config.js (custom colors, fonts)
└─ README.md

All routes (/(public)/, /admin/, /pro/) use same design tokens.
Consistency enforced at build time.
```

