## NO SHARED CODE

**Critical rule:**

Launch website and Match 2.0 have **zero shared code**, **zero shared database**, **zero shared infrastructure**.

- Separate git repos
- Separate deployment systems
- Separate authentication
- Separate data

This ensures:
- ✅ Launch can be archived without affecting Match 2.0
