**Key Decisions:**
- Unified Next.js application (vs. separate services)
- Supabase backend (PostgreSQL + Auth + RLS)
- Separated SessionLog (documentation) from RegisteredHours (time tracking)
- CaseGrant model (municipal budget per period)
