### Professional Management (2 entities)

**Professional**
```
├─ id: UUID (FK to profiles, 1:1)
├─ profession: TEACHER | PEDAGOGUE | NURSE | PSYCHOLOGIST | SOCIAL_WORKER | COUNSELOR | OTHER
├─ experience_years: Int
